Introduction

Sphaze, previously known as Oort Boys before debuting, is a virtual group under Oort Entertainment. It consists of five members (Do Minseong, Nithan, Frederic, Ma Daehyeop, and Seo Tale) who were revealed one after another.

On July 30, 2024, Oort Ent. revealed the name of the group to be Sphaze. Their name is short for "Special Phaze."

They debuted on September 30, 2024, with their first single album, Starlight.
